# well-spelled: include
#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reduce the number of #includes in &kde; source files"
msgstr ""
"Reduce o número de directrices «#include» nos ficheiros de fontes de &kde;."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> <group><option>-v, --verbose</option></group> "
"<group><option>-e, --experimental</option></group> <group><option>-m, --"
"modify</option></group> <group><option><replaceable>file</replaceable></"
"option></group> <group><option>--help</option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> <group><option>-v, --verbose</option></group> "
"<group><option>-e, --experimental</option></group> <group><option>-m, --"
"modify</option></group> <group><option><replaceable>ficheiro</replaceable></"
"option></group> <group><option>--help</option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descrición"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> tries to reduce the number of #includes in C+"
"+ source files. Much of it's processing is specific to &kde; sources and so "
"it might not work so well with sources for non-&kde; applications."
msgstr ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> intenta reducir o número de #includes nos "
"ficheiros de fontes de C++. Grande parte do que fai é específico para as "
"fontes de &kde; polo que posibelmente non traballe tan ben con fontes de "
"aplicacións que non sexan de &kde;."

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following problems are identified by <command>fixincludes</command>:"
msgstr ""
"Identificáronse os seguintes problemas de <command>fixincludes</command>:"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Including headers that are no longer supported but which exist for "
"compatibility with older Qt/KDE versions;"
msgstr ""
"Incluír cabeceiras que deixaron de estar permitidos pero que existen por "
"compatibilidades con versións anteriores de Qt/KDE;"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Including the same file multiple times."
msgstr "Incluír o mesmo ficheiro múltiplas veces."

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also an experimental mode which tries removing each #include one at "
"a time (with a few exceptions) to see whether the source still compiles. "
"Note that this experimental mode will modify the original sources."
msgstr ""
"Tamén hai un modo experimental que intenta retirar un #include de cada vez "
"(cunhas poucas excepcións) para ver se as fontes aínda compilan. Lembre que "
"este é un modo experimental que modificará as fontes orixinais."

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default the sources will not be modified; the identified problems will "
"simply be written to standard output."
msgstr ""
"De maneira predeterminada, as fontes non se modificarán; os problemas que se "
"identifiquen notificaranse pola saída estándar."

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list of C++ sources to examine should be given on the command-line. If "
"no files are given, all C++ sources in or beneath the current directory will "
"be examined (with the exception of directories whose <filename>Makefile.am</"
"filename> contains <option>-UQT_NO_COMPAT</option> or <option>-"
"UKDE_NO_COMPAT</option>)"
msgstr ""
"A lista de fontes C++ a examinar debe indicarse na liña de ordes. Se non "
"indica ningún ficheiro, todas as fontes C++ dentro ou baixo o cartafol "
"actual examinaranse (coa excepción dos cartafoles nos que o seu ficheiro "
"<filename>Makefile.am</filename> conteña a opción <option>-UQT_NO_COMPAT</"
"option> ou <option>-UKDE_NO_COMPAT</option>)"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the KDE Software Development Kit."
msgstr ""
"Esta utilidade forma parte do equipamento de desenvolvemento de programas de "
"KDE."

#. Tag: title
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opcións"

#. Tag: option
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v, --verbose"
msgstr "-v, --verbose"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Verbose mode. Additional debugging output is written to standard output."
msgstr ""
"Modo verboso. Amósase información adicional de depuración pola saída "
"estándar."

#. Tag: option
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "-e, --experimental"
msgstr "-e, --experimental"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Experimental mode, as described above in detail. Note that this option "
"implies <option>--modify</option>."
msgstr ""
"Modo experimental, definido en detalle anteriormente. Lembre que esta opción "
"implica un <option>--modify</option>."

#. Tag: option
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "-m, --modify"
msgstr "-m, --modify"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As well as writing messages to standard output, actually modify the original "
"sources to fix any problems that were found."
msgstr ""
"Ademais de escribir na saída estándar, modificará de verdade as fontes "
"orixinais para corrixir os problemas que fosen atopados."

#. Tag: title
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Authors"
msgstr "Autoría"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> was written by Dirk Mueller "
"<email>mueller@kde.org</email>."
msgstr ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> foi escrito por Dirk Mueller "
"<email>mueller@kde.org</email>."

